{"nodes": [{"id": "docs_gdd_00_vision_la_direction", "label": "La Direction", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/gdd/00-vision.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Entite du jeu qui murmure les offres secretes (Pactes). Voix TTS corporate froide et polie, contraste comique avec le chaos; pour les streamers, La Direction = la production de l'emission."}, {"id": "docs_gdd_00_vision_piliers_de_design", "label": "Les 4 piliers de design", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "docs/gdd/00-vision.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "1) Deni plausible (regle n.1, chaque systeme audite contre elle); 2) Le mensonge est score; 3) Perdre doit etre drole (retention entre amis); 4) Le jeu fabrique ses propres clips (viralite = feature budgetee, pas du marketing)."}, {"id": "docs_gdd_00_vision_lethal_company", "label": "Lethal Company", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/gdd/00-vision.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Reference: on prend le loot physique, le quota, l'esthetique, la voix de proximite. On rejette le bestiaire couteux de monstres."}, {"id": "docs_gdd_00_vision_among_us", "label": "Among Us", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/gdd/00-vision.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Reference: le moment d'ejection comme format de clip, la paranoia. On rejette l'absence de physique et d'argent."}, {"id": "docs_gdd_00_vision_terminal_de_michou", "label": "Le Terminal de Michou", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/gdd/00-vision.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Reference culturelle FR-first: dilemmes secrets a